    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the MIB module for the Digital Video Broadcasting Return Channel via Satellite system (DVB-RCS), as defined by the SatLabs Group.  It defines a set of MIB objects to characterize the behavior and performance of network-layer entities deploying DVB-RCS.  This document is not an Internet Standards Track specification; it is published for informational purposes.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
